{"tid":1004201,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中原CCL最新報170.86點按周升0.13% 有尋底成功跡象","createTime":"2019-02-01T09:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T10:27:01.000Z","uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"61accbc31cd32e7ec15b74a8b98c9c93b0847e87","tid":1004201,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://plib.aastocks.com/aafnnews/image/medialib/20180119145750962_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplib.aastocks.com%2Faafnnews%2Fimage%2Fmedialib%2F20180119145750962_l.jpg&h=c2912d6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中原城市領先指數CCL最新報170.86點，按周升0.13%。中原地產研究部高級聯席董事黃良昇指出，CCL兩周前跌幅明顯收窄，之後連續2周上升。近3周CCL持續在170點窄幅徘徊，未有進一步下跌，有尋底成功的跡象。如果未來數周CCL可以企穩170點以上，新春前後樓價有望確認止跌回穩。<br />\n<br />\n1月4日人行宣布降準後，三大整體指數齊升2周，是26周以來首見，即六招房策公布後再現。CCL連續2周累升0.40%，CCL Mass升0.5%，CCL(中小型單位)升0.45%。中原城市大型屋苑領先指數CCL Mass報171.84點，按周升0.2%。CCL(中小型單位)報170.50點，按周升0.18%。<br />\n<br />\nCCL(大型單位)報172.7點，按周跌0.08%。近3周豪宅樓價在172點反覆徘徊。<br />\n<br />\n四區樓價方面，本周二升二跌。九龍CCL Mass報167.98點，按周升0.8%，連升2周共0.86%。新界西CCL Mass報156.82點，按周升1.82%，結束3周連跌。港島CCL Mass報178.18點，按周跌0.41%。新界東CCL Mass報176.26點，按周跌2.22%。<br />\n<br />\n今天(2019年2月1日)公布的指數，根據2019年1月21日至1月27日簽訂正式買賣合約的中原集團成交計算。當中有近八成的交易是在2019年1月7日至1月13日簽臨時買賣合約。1月31日美國聯儲局維持利率不變及有機會減慢縮表步伐，對香港樓市的影響將於2019年2月下旬的CCL才開始反映。(ac/lf)"},{"pid":"d78ec2dc8490f5866018241e4e5c9936c9bebeee","tid":1004201,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:18:37.000Z","msg":"淡友呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299e7758eacc3fff4ceab75994eedf0f69ecb4d7","tid":1004201,"uid":19725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:28:28.000Z","msg":"鑽石黃金鋼鐵鈦金屬底 170！！！！"},{"pid":"dcd407f7a7815ed67451b4ae460418ac9758ecc3","tid":1004201,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"大爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4393986ececb904c04c544ddbe1286bce0fd256","tid":1004201,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd407f7a7815ed67451b4ae460418ac9758ecc3","tid":1004201,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"大爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}